Date: Fri, 20 Aug 2021 17:49:58 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] s32v234hpcsom: add defconfig

Add defconfig for s32v234hpcsom board.

Issue: ALB-7473

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Radu Pirea (NXP OSS) radu-nicolae.pirea@oss.nxp.com
Signed-off-by: Zhantao Tang <zhantao.tang@windriver.com>
---
 configs/s32v234hpcsom_defconfig | 25 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 25 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 configs/s32v234hpcsom_defconfig

diff --git a/configs/s32v234hpcsom_defconfig b/configs/s32v234hpcsom_defconfig
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..8dda41587e
--- /dev/null
+++ b/configs/s32v234hpcsom_defconfig
@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@
+CONFIG_ARM=y
+CONFIG_ARCH_S32=y
+CONFIG_ENV_SIZE=0x2000
+CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET=0x100000
+CONFIG_NR_DRAM_BANKS=3
+CONFIG_TARGET_S32V234HPCSOM=y
+CONFIG_DISTRO_DEFAULTS=y
+# CONFIG_SYS_MALLOC_F is not set
+CONFIG_SD_BOOT=y
+CONFIG_USE_BOOTARGS=y
+CONFIG_ARCH_EARLY_INIT_R=y
+CONFIG_BOARD_EARLY_INIT_F=y
+CONFIG_CMD_I2C=y
+CONFIG_CMD_MMC=y
+CONFIG_CMD_PCI=y
+CONFIG_ENV_IS_IN_MMC=y
+CONFIG_DM=y
+CONFIG_FSL_CSE3=y
+CONFIG_FSL_USDHC=y
+CONFIG_FEC_MXC=y
+CONFIG_RGMII=y
+CONFIG_MII=y
+CONFIG_FSL_LINFLEXUART=y
+CONFIG_OF_LIBFDT=y
+CONFIG_FSL_DCU_FB=y
